    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Yes, basically, when it try to calculate the new state, because the number is serialized the sum is wrong:\r\n\r\n```\r\np=0\r\np=01\r\np=011\r\np=0111\r\n```\r\n\r\nexpected (and the thing that this issue resolve)\r\n\r\n```\r\np=0\r\np=1\r\np=2\r\np=3\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
    "created_at": "2016-11-28T15:11:47Z",
